エリカ HK_PT01-1

\n< Serena >Hoo... I never knew there was such a
path in the forest... This is indeed
easy to walk on.

\n< Serena >With this, I can return earlier than
planned. Thank you, Eri...
\n< Serena >What's with that face?

\n< Erika >Ne-ne-Serena-chan. Let's have a love
chat- a love chat-
\n< Serena >What's that... I refuse.
\n< Erika >Don't you have someone you like-?
\n< Serena >You're persistent... No, I don't.
\n< Serena >Hmm... Ah... But I did have a fiancé.
\n< Erika >Eh!?
\n< Erika >Shh! Shushushu! Shh! Shh!
\n< Serena >What's that supposed to be?

\n< Erika >Hey boy! If you want to date Serena-
chan, you'll have to defeat me first!
\n< Serena >You intend to fight...

\n< Serena >Well, no need to worry. He's already
passed away.
\n< Erika >Eh...
\n< Erika >That... sorry... I...
\n< Serena >Hm? Oh, it's not like that.

\n< Serena >He was a stranger. It was an arrangement
between families.

\n< Serena >One day suddenly I was told I was
engaged to this person... It must have
been about half a year later.

\n< Serena >Being from a distant place, we hardly
had the chance to meet, and then I
received news that he had died of an
epidemic.

\n< Serena >After all, I didn't even know his face
or voice, so it's not like I could cry
over it.

\n< Serena >...That's about all there is to my
romantic affairs.
\n< Erika >That's... but still... my condolences...

\n< Serena >There's no wound to grieve over. Though
I do feel pity...

Speaking of pity... The one who was most
troubled by his death must have been
none other than my father.\n< Serena >
\n< Erika >Your dad?

Currently in our house, the only
potential heirs are my sister and me.
We're what you'd call female heirs.\n< Serena >

Needless to say, in our country, male
primogeniture is the norm. Therefore,
the current situation of our house
without a male child is somewhat...
extremely bad.\n< Serena >

That's why, ideally, I should marry as
soon as possible and bear a male child.\n< Serena >

If either my sister or I can bear a male
child while my father is still alive, he
can pass on the family estate to that
child and everything will be settled
smoothly.\n< Serena >

\n< Serena >However, it's not as if any groom will
do.

Preferably someone from among our
relatives, and as distantly related by
blood as possible.\n< Serena >

The man who fit those conditions was my
fiancé. Father went through quite a lot
of trouble in the negotiations for our
engagement.\n< Serena >

Just when everything was finally about
to be realized, it all fell through
because of the cancellation.\n< Serena >

One can only imagine the stress on my
father as the head of the family.\n< Serena >

\n< Erika >What about you, Serena? Your family is
in danger, right?

True... Honestly, there was a part of me
that was relieved. Not that I'm glad he
died or anything.\n< Serena >

The thought of suddenly becoming husband
and wife with a man I don't know... It's
purely terrifying.\n< Serena >

But it's our duty to continue the family
line and pass on the blood. I also think
that we must bear children no matter
what.\n< Serena >
So, well. It's complicated.\n< Serena >

One thing I can say is that if I had
married him, I wouldn't be here like
this right now.\n< Serena >

I'm not trying to argue whether that's
good or bad, but I want to do the best I
can with the situation given to me.\n< Serena >

Father would probably find this way of
thinking laughable.\n< Serena >

\n< Erika >You're supposed to be quietly staying at
home, huh.

However, I do have an older sister at
home.\n< Serena >

Her marriage has been decided. The
negotiations are difficult because her
partner is from another family...\n< Serena >

But if it's my sister, she will
ultimately take control of the
situation.\n< Serena >

She is a person of much higher caliber
than I am. After all, I am merely a
spare for her.\n< Serena >

\n< Erika >That's not a good way to talk about
yourself, you know? That would make your
parents the saddest!
\n< Serena >...Is that so?
\n< Erika >Of course it is.

\n< Erika >I've also run away from home, so I won't
say to return immediately or anything...

\n< Erika >But why don't you find that Unicorn-chan
quickly and go back to show your parents
and sister that you're safe and sound?
\n< Erika >Then get scolded a whole lot!

\n< Serena >Fufu, that's true. It would be nice if a
spanking was all it took.
\n< Erika >Oh! You laughed! Serena-chan smiled!

\n< Serena >...I do laugh when something is funny.
Was I really that stern-faced...?
エリカ HK_PT01-1
エリカ HK_PT01-1
\n< Erika >Alright. The highway is in sight.

\n< Erika >If we've come this far, there's no need
to worry anymore.
\n< Serena >"Anymore"...?
\n< Erika >Ah. Oops...

\n< Serena >So you were escorting me after all. I
thought it might be something like
that...
\n< Erika >Sorry... I was just worried...

\n< Serena >...Well, it's fine. I've gotten used to
being treated like a child by you.

Although it's regrettable, it's also a
fact that I've been helped by you time
and again.\n< Serena >

It seems I must show you that I can be
of help to you as well, to satisfy you.\n< Serena >
\n< Erika >It's not like that but...

\n< Serena >In any case, this shortcut was helpful.
For that, I'll honestly thank you.

\n< Serena >However, it's like a tunnel in the
middle of the forest. If such a
convenient path existed, Master should
have told me about it...

\n< Erika >Nah, the folks in town don't like to use
this place. It's actually a bit
dangerous too. That's why I came with
you.
\n< Serena >What do you mean?

\n< Erika >This is the path the Minotaur took after
passing through here.

\n< Erika >In an excited state, that is, when it
came to attack the town.

\n< Erika >If it's passed through once, there's a
chance it might come out again.

\n< Serena >...Ridiculous. This is? Just the
destruction left by a single monster...?
※カメラ上のほうまでスクロール

\n< Erika >Looks like we could use some military
hardware, right?
\n< Serena >...

\V[2501]\n< Serena >With this, we're only a few more tasks
away from our goal. Thanks to Lord
Erika, it seems we can accomplish one
more task today.
...\n< Serena >
'　エリカ殿の案内のおかげで早めに帰ってこられた。'
'　これなら今日中にもう一つくらい仕事をこなせるだろう。ギルドへ向かおう。'

events.name: 第一部ラストイベント　移動

\n< Serena >...It seems it will still take some time
to get through the forest. I hope Erika-
sama is safe...

\n< Serena >However, to save someone else only to be
captured herself... That's so like
Erika-sama...

\n< Serena >Come to think of it, I was saved by
Erika-sama in this forest before... So
now, it's my turn to do the same!
\n< Serena >I will definitely save her...!
